        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Adam’s Revenge: Ending Tibor&apos;s New Pawn",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131801139667",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository c76452de-4e87-463e-92f6-42a442669202).Image",
        "Description": "Adam believes his parents, Tibor and Sanyi, despise him because their divorce tore the family apart. Convinced that Tibor left Sanyi for his new wife, Adam initially fantasizes about making her suffer, blaming her for the breakup. However, he soon realizes that she’s just a pawn in the larger scheme. Choosing a swift and merciful approach, Adam decides to give her a quick death—a single bullet to the head, putting an end to the pain she unknowingly caused. I will leave you to prepare!",
